类 DepthFirstVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • visitor.DepthFirstVisitor
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Visitor

    public class DepthFirstVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor
    Provides default methods which visit each node in the tree in depth-first order. Your visitors may extend this class.
